      </p>
      <p begin="03:21.881" end="03:26.471" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38">
        <span begin="03:21.881" end="03:26.471">Aku tetap sama</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="03:27.119" end="03:35.039" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39">
        <span begin="03:27.119" end="03:35.039">Yang berubah justru kau yang kusandar</span>
